- decisions: geometry=procedural CylinderGeometry (no GLB); single 2048² CanvasTexture compositor with FRONT px512–1536 / BACK px0–512+1536–2048; meshPhysicalMaterial(sheen0.9/rough0.85) + studio Environment + Poly Haven knit normal map + ContactShadows; @imgly/background-removal lazy WASM refine over always-on alpha-bbox; per-image zoom/offset/rotation sliders.
- next needs: demo-builder edits ShirtCanvas/OptionsPanel/store + adds compositor.ts & smartAlign.ts per the touch map; CORS-check the Poly Haven URL (vendor jpg if it fails); rebuild + deploy-test the wrap + smart-align flow.
- risks: side-seam distortion on non-tiling photos (mirror-seam toggle mitigates); @imgly 12MB first-load latency (spinner + instant deterministic); recomposite must stay <100ms (rAF throttle + 16ms debounce); collar/placket fidelity is geometry+material only (no UV detail).

